
# <emoji> <type>(<scope>): <summary>
#   ✨ feat(auth): add OAuth2 login   ·   🐛 fix(api): handle null token
#
# ── Subject ── imperative · Capitalized · no period · ≤ 50 chars ──────────────
#          1         2         3         4         5
# 12345678901234567890123456789012345678901234567890
#
# ── Body ── what & why (not how) · blank line above · wrap at 72 ──────────────
#          1         2         3         4         5         6         7
# 123456789012345678901234567890123456789012345678901234567890123456789012
#
#
# ── Footer (optional) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#   BREAKING CHANGE: <what breaks and how to migrate>
#   Closes #123   ·   Refs #456
#   Co-authored-by: Name <user@users.noreply.github.com>
#
# ── Types ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#   ✨ feat      new feature              ⚡ perf      performance
#   🐛 fix       bug fix                  ✅ test      add / fix tests
#   📝 docs      documentation            🔧 chore     tooling · deps · chores
#   📚 refactor  behaviour-neutral edit   👷 ci        CI / CD pipelines
#   💄 style     formatting only          🔒 security  security fix
#   🚑 hotfix    urgent production fix     ⏪ revert    undo a previous commit
#
# A good subject completes: "If applied, this commit will <subject>".
# Guide → https://chris.beams.io/posts/git-commit/
